RFID::Reader version 0.01
========================

this perl module is an interface to the RFID 13.56 MHz
ISO15693-Reader shipped by Megaset Systemtechnik.

directory 'tools/' contains a simple command line script,
that uses RFID::Reader functionality to communicate with
ISO15693 transponders via controller.

SUPPORTED PLATTFORMS

- Mac OS X (tested)
- FreeBSD (should work)
- Linux (should work)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Device::SerialPort.

